<h2 id="concept">Concept</h2>

<p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=helixquar.asciidecorator">ASCII Decorator</a> is an extension for VS Code and others that allows you to transform words to look neat. This can make it easier, for example, when you want a better view of your code, a separation of snippets that make it easier to find, for example:</p>

