<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>

<p>To install on VS Code is very simple, follow the steps:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>1.</strong> Open your editor;</li>
  <li><strong>2.</strong> Click Extensions, or simply press: <code class="highlighter-rouge">Ctrl + shift + X</code>;</li>
  <li><strong>3.</strong> And in the search field, type: ASCIIDecorator, see image below:</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/dev/ASCIIDecotaror-extension.png" alt="ASCII Decorator" /></p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>4.</strong> E ent√£o clique em <button style="background: green; color: #fff;border:none;">Install</button> .</li>
</ul>

